    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Scottish caps of varying forms, but without brim or visor, usually of knitted wool; originally worn by people in the military.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
